      "source": [
        "# Imageboard Dataset Explorer\n",
        "\n",
        "This notebook provides a comprehensive guide for exploring, analyzing, and mining the 4chan imageboard dataset. The dataset is stored as a single self-contained Parquet file with embedded images and HTML.\n",
        "\n",
        "## What's Included\n",
        "- **Post Metadata**: Board, thread ID, post numbers, timestamps\n",
        "- **Content**: Post comments, thread subjects\n",
        "- **Embedded Images**: Raw image bytes for every post with images\n",
        "- **Original HTML**: Full thread HTML for deep analysis\n",
        "- **Moderation Data**: Quality flags and reasons for filtering\n",
        "\n",
        "## Quick Start\n",
        "```python\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "df = pd.read_parquet('imageboard_full_embed_20260105.parquet')\n",
        "print(f\"Loaded {len(df)} posts with {df['image_bytes'].notna().sum()} images\")\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "## Table of Contents\n",
        "1. Loading & Basic Exploration\n",
        "2. Image Viewing & Manipulation\n",
        "3. Text Analysis & Search\n",
        "4. Filtering & Aggregation\n",
        "5. Visualizations\n",
        "6. ML Pipeline Example: Face Detection\n",
        "7. Exporting Subsets\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# Setup and Configuration\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "from pathlib import Path\n",
        "from PIL import Image\n",
        "import io\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "from datetime import datetime\n",
        "import warnings\n",
        "warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\n",
        "\n",
        "# Find the parquet file\n",
        "PARQUET_PATHS = [\n",
        "    Path('/home/jovyan/workspaces/packs/imageboard_full_embed_20260105.parquet'),\n",
        "    Path('/home/warby/Workspace/jupyter/packs/imageboard_full_embed_20260105.parquet'),\n",
        "    Path('./packs/imageboard_full_embed_20260105.parquet'),\n",
        "    Path('./imageboard_full_embed_latest.parquet'),\n",
        "]\n",
        "\n",
        "PARQUET_FILE = None\n",
        "for p in PARQUET_PATHS:\n",
        "    if p.exists():\n",
        "        PARQUET_FILE = p\n",
        "        break\n",
        "\n",
        "if PARQUET_FILE:\n",
        "    print(f\"✓ Found dataset: {PARQUET_FILE.name}\")\n",
        "    print(f\"  Size: {PARQUET_FILE.stat().st_size / (1024**2):.1f} MB\")\n",
        "else:\n",
        "    print(\"⚠ Dataset not found. Please update PARQUET_FILE path.\")\n",
        "    print(\"  Expected locations:\")\n",
        "    for p in PARQUET_PATHS:\n",
        "        print(f\"    - {p}\")\n"
      ]
    },
    {
